  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of STX209 (Arbaclofen) for Social Withdrawal in Adolescents and Adults With Fragile X Syndrome</brief_title>
  <acronym>Harbor-A</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study of the Efficacy, Safety, and Tolerability of STX209 (Arbaclofen) Administered for the Treatment of Social Function in Adolescents and Adults With Fragile X Syndrome</official_title>
